  <text>
    <body>
      <div type="cap" n="1" xml:id="CID001">
        <p><milestone unit="par" n="1"/>Nobis autem euntibus peruenimus ad quendam locum, ubi se tamen montes illi aperientes faciebant uallem infinitam.</p>
        <p><milestone unit="par" n="2"/>Vallis autem ipsa ingens est ualde, iacens subter latus montis Dei.</p>
      </div>
      <div type="cap" n="2" xml:id="CID002">
        <p><milestone unit="par" n="1"/>Itaque ergo sabbato sera ingressi sumus montem et peruenimus ad monasteria quaedam.</p>
      </div>
      <div type="cap" n="3" xml:id="CID003">
        <p><milestone unit="par" n="1"/>Ipse autem <supplied>locus</supplied> in extremo iam montis est. <note>Textual note here.</note></p>
      </div>
    </body>
  </text>
